@TITLE "rzxtool(1)ĀmanualĀpage"
 @{" " link "'#toc'/MAIN"}Table of Contents

 @{" " link "'#toc0'/MAIN"}Name rzxtool - Modify properties Sinclair ZX Spectrum input recording files @{" " link "'#toc1'/MAIN"}Synopsis @{"b"}rzxtool@{"ub"} [-a @{"i"}snapfile@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} [ -e ] [ -r ] [ -u ] @{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"} 

@{" " link "'#toc2'/MAIN"}Description Rzxtool allows modification or extraction of the snapshot embedded in an RZX input recording file and/or (un)compression of the data stored in the file. @{" " link "'#toc3'/MAIN"}Options @{"i"}-a@{"ui"} snapfile The snapshot specified in @{"i"}snapfile@{"ui"} will be added to the RZX file, replacing any snapshot which is currently present in @{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"}. The new RZX file will be output to standard output. @{"i"}snapfile@{"ui"} can be any of the .sna, .snp, .sp, .szx, .z80, .zxs or +D formats. 

@{"i"}-e@{"ui"} The snapshot present in @{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"} will be output to standard output in .z80 format. This option is incompatible with the @{"i"}-a@{"ui"}, @{"i"}-r@{"ui"} and @{"i"}-u@{"ui"} options. 

@{"i"}-r@{"ui"} Any snapshot present in @{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"} will be removed, and the new RZX file output to standard output. 

@{"i"}-u@{"ui"} When outputting an RZX file, this option causes the input recording data to be output uncompressed; if this option is not given, the data will be compressed using @{" " link "'zlib.3'/MAIN"}@{"i"}zlib@{"ui"}(3) . 

@{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"} specifies an input recording file whose contents are to be modified. @{" " link "'#toc4'/MAIN"}Bugs None known @{" " link "'#toc5'/MAIN"}See Also @{" " link "'fuse.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'fuse-utils.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse-utils@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'rzxcheck.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}rzxcheck@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'rzxdump.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}rzxdump@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'zlib.3'/MAIN"}@{"i"}zlib@{"ui"}(3) 

The comp.sys.sinclair Spectrum FAQ, at 
@{" " link "'http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html.guide/MAIN"}@{"i"}http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html@{"ui"}. @{" " link "'#toc6'/MAIN"}Author Philip Kendall (philip-fuse@shadowmagic.org.uk). 


